org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.rank

Class RankState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.rank.RankState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class RankState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A rank state represents a state in the rank-based complementation, including a subset of the source states (set S), s subset of set S (set O), a rank function f: Q -> {0..max_rank}. f maps accepting states to only even numbers.
    Author:
    Yi-Wen Chang
